  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631670/extras/29e369975d68532811bac3e4d88184ef.avif?t=1762274845\" width=616 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631670/extras/1fd82f2847cc3d694a88a81238fd50fe.poster.avif?t=1762274845\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631670/extras/1fd82f2847cc3d694a88a81238fd50fe.webm?t=1762274845\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631670/extras/1fd82f2847cc3d694a88a81238fd50fe.mp4?t=1762274845\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Surround your opponent with pieces, obstacles, and summons to instantly eliminate enemy pieces, including bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This tactic works even against multiple players in a single encirclement.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631670/extras/8a1b66c5fe58f17aeb0efa0a329b51e7.poster.avif?t=1762274845\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631670/extras/8a1b66c5fe58f17aeb0efa0a329b51e7.webm?t=1762274845\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631670/extras/8a1b66c5fe58f17aeb0efa0a329b51e7.mp4?t=1762274845\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631670/extras/505b657e54728777bbc01bfa31c0b259.avif?t=1762274845\" width=616 height=100 /></span>In a distant future, the world has been destroyed by war and pollution.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A self-proclaimed goddess, Yarno, has established a laboratory in the snowy wilderness and orchestrated a game of mutual slaughter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players take on the role of a tribe's leader, who must protect their people while also unraveling the truth behind this deadly game...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631670/extras/ec5da4fb0a6bb8551f3c30522def2c38.avif?t=1762274845\" width=616 height=346 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631670/extras/bf29f3a007eea501fb60a0aaaae5faee.avif?t=1762274845\" width=616 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631670/extras/389bbfa1c691e316a2fced9a30ee92e0.avif?t=1762274845\" width=616 height=346 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631670/extras/516bf5b13e05ad5f75765859d9a5b94a.avif?t=1762274845\" width=616 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631670/extras/584859705ba3d26e7d42ae90c7fa534a.poster.avif?t=1762274845\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631670/extras/584859705ba3d26e7d42ae90c7fa534a.webm?t=1762274845\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631670/extras/584859705ba3d26e7d42ae90c7fa534a.mp4?t=1762274845\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https: